    <li><a href="https://www.fisherpaykel.com/au/laundry/dryers/condensing/condensing-dryer-8kg-de8060p3-93280.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fisher &amp; Paykel DE8060P3 specifications</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.appliancesonline.com.au/product/fisher-paykel-8kg-condenser-dryer-de8060p3/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Appliances Online DE8060P3 owner reviews</a></li>
